_sText:
There are many places to explore and hide in this map, so it's never the same game twice. Where will you hide?
( Just for fun, I hid 5 bananas in this map. Can you find them?...yeah probably.)
The map has 42 Spawn points. I recommend as much players as you can get. 

Feel free to edit this map if you wish, just give credit. 
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Update:
-Fixed CT buy zone
-Built cube maps
-Elevator's fubar so I slapped a ladder in there.
